    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Unfortunately, you are in Hell</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3295990/extras/0c3991364ecf22cbd0acf4070100c6df.avif?t=1731349813\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3295990/extras_big/0c3991364ecf22cbd0acf4070100c6df.avif?t=1731349813 width=800 height=418 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You find yourself in a land full of lava, fire, and vegetables?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You have been selected for the opportunity to serve the devil himself, and perhaps earn your freedom from damnation.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Follow the recipe!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3295990/extras/1b2b7263a2a9ae6db573e18f6272ca90.avif?t=1731349813\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3295990/extras_big/1b2b7263a2a9ae6db573e18f6272ca90.avif?t=1731349813 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Thanks to those countless fools who came before you, Satan's tastes are refined and demanding. Do not disappoint. Your task will be easy... as long as you follow the recipe. Read the instructions or face his wrath and hunger.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3295990/extras/4edadbc34a37db8ab0f3370cf715e6c8.avif?t=1731349813\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3295990/extras_big/4edadbc34a37db8ab0f3370cf715e6c8.avif?t=1731349813 width=800 height=254 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The pantry comes magically stocked with everything you will need.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Prepare your dish!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3295990/extras/187719ae2cd37d6fc9c886dc376c16a8.poster.avif?t=1731349813\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3295990/extras/187719ae2cd37d6fc9c886dc376c16a8.webm?t=1731349813\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3295990/extras/187719ae2cd37d6fc9c886dc376c16a8.mp4?t=1731349813\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3295990/extras/d1602c1ae2bc3382a86bff29dfe25941.poster.avif?t=1731349813\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3295990/extras/d1602c1ae2bc3382a86bff29dfe25941.webm?t=1731349813\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3295990/extras/d1602c1ae2bc3382a86bff29dfe25941.mp4?t=1731349813\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3295990/extras/ae10cf593173b2a2b171c9b22580e5e0.poster.avif?t=1731349813\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3295990/extras/ae10cf593173b2a2b171c9b22580e5e0.webm?t=1731349813\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3295990/extras/ae10cf593173b2a2b171c9b22580e5e0.mp4?t=1731349813\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Chop, fry, and plate your ingredients in the kitchen!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Defend your ingredients!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3295990/extras/6946e32546d2da72f075fa0ed846230a.poster.avif?t=1731349813\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3295990/extras/6946e32546d2da72f075fa0ed846230a.webm?t=1731349813\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3295990/extras/6946e32546d2da72f075fa0ed846230a.mp4?t=1731349813\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3295990/extras/ba1dad42b00b6b9efb38d5902d812150.poster.avif?t=1731349813\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3295990/extras/ba1dad42b00b6b9efb38d5902d812150.webm?t=1731349813\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3295990/extras/ba1dad42b00b6b9efb38d5902d812150.mp4?t=1731349813\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Mischievous imps will do their best to get in your way. Stop them from stealing your ingredients (and maybe throw them in the lava while you're at it).</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Finish before the time runs out!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3295990/extras/4ee440c624d3a24f272ce0d7d97e93a7.avif?t=1731349813\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3295990/extras_big/4ee440c624d3a24f272ce0d7d97e93a7.avif?t=1731349813 width=800 height=450 /></span>As you cook the lava will rise; submit everything before the time runs out! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If Satan's appetite isn't satisfied, who knows what he'll do!</p>",
